Use Case : Mange project information

 

Title: Mange project information

Primary Actor: Corporate Manager

Goal in Context: Corporate Manager should to manage code information.

Stakeholders: Corporate manager and corporate developer.

Preconditions: The project file exists in the SPDX database.

Main Success Scenario: Corporate manager obtains and manages project information.

Failed End Conditions: Corporate manager is fails to manage project information.

Trigger: Corporate manager wants to manage a project.

Use Case: Determine License and Vulnerability Information

¡  Title: Determine License and Vulnerability Information

¡  Primary Actor: Corporate Manager

¡  Goal in Context: The corporate manager is able to determine license and vulnerability information from provided project information

¡  Stakeholders:

¡  Corporate Manager: To receive clear and relevant project information

¡  Corporate Developer: To provide the relevant file/package level information

¡  Project Owner: To clearly understand corporate manager decisions to green/red light a project

¡  Preconditions:

¡  Relevant file/package information is in the SPDX database

¡  Proper project information has been provided 

¡  Main Success Scenario: Corporate manager receives accurate license and vulnerability information for the requested project packages

¡  Failed End Conditions: Corporate manager receives inaccurate or invalid license and vulnerability information for the requested project packages

¡  Trigger: Corporate manager uploads or identifies project information to which license and vulnerability information is provided

 

Use Case: Manage code

¡  Title: Manage code

¡  Primary Actor: Corporate Manager and developer

¡  Goal in Context: The corporate manager/developer is able to determine and manage code

¡  Stakeholders:

¡  Corporate Manager: To receive clear and relevant project information and code information

¡  Corporate Developer: To provide the relevant file/package level information

¡  Project Owner: To clearly understand corporate manager decisions to green/red light a project

¡  Preconditions:

¡  Relevant file/package information is available

¡  Main Success Scenario: Corporate manager and developer receive accurate code information.

¡  Failed End Conditions: Corporate manager receives inaccurate or invalid license and vulnerability information for the requested project packages

¡  Trigger: Corporate manager and developer a file/package to manage code.

 
 
